text: Novoyakupovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Kanzafarovsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 26 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Zilair, 2 km from Yumaguzhino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Novoyakupovo
